channel.description:
[b][size=15pt]Please do [u]NOT[/u] call me a noob because I don't understand this error![/size][/b]

So I was changing my server to have Silabsoft's updated client work on it, so I changed everything and got this error:
[code]client.java:13198: ')' expected if (addItem((bank[fromSlot],amount)) ^[/code]
I don't know how to fix and this is stopping the other stuff that I coded to get the stuff working from sucsesfully working.
So please can someone give me advice or maybe the correct code that goes here? By the way, this is in my [i]client.java[/i] but you probably knew that.
Thanks, [size=15pt]I Fix I[/size]
